<%- include("template/headers") %>

<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1 class="display-3 text-center p-3" style="color: white;">Calculadora para Freelance</h1>
    <hr class="m-0" style="color:aquamarine"><br><br>
    <p class="lead col-8 mx-auto text-center " style="color: white;"><b>Si usted es un programador freelance, sabiendo que muchas veces
            las ofertas
            laborales se expresan en valor hora, le traiga aqui la solución a saber cuanto va a cobrar por semana, mes y
            año,
            lo unico que necesitamos para empezar es saber el valor de la hora.</b></p><br><br><br>
</div>
<form action="", method='post'>
    <fieldset class="input-group w-25 m-auto">
        <div class="input-group w-75 m-auto">
            <span class="input-group-text" id="addon-wrapping">u$d</span>
            <input id="valor" name="cantidad" type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="0.00" aria-label="valorH" aria-describedby="addon-wrapping">
        </div>
        <div class="input-group w-25 m-auto">
            <button id="btn" type="button" class="btn btn-dark" name="boton">Calcular</button>
        </div>      
    </fieldset>
    <br><br><br>
    <div class="input-group w-25 m-auto">
        <span class="input-group-text w-25" id="addon-wrapping">Semana</span> 
        <output id="semana" name="result" type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="0.00" aria-label="valorH" aria-describedby="addon-wrapping" >
    </div><br>
    <div class="input-group w-25 m-auto">
        <span class="input-group-text w-25" id="addon-wrapping">Mes</span> 
        <output id="mes" name="result" type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="0.00" aria-label="valorH" aria-describedby="addon-wrapping" >
    </div><br>
    <div class="input-group w-25 m-auto">
        <span class="input-group-text w-25"  id="addon-wrapping">Año</span> 
        <output id="anio" name="result" type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="0.00" aria-label="valorH" aria-describedby="addon-wrapping" >
    </div>   
</form>

<script src="template/script.js"></script>